Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: Intel: cml_rt1011_rt5682: fix codec_conf by removing legacy style
Git-commit: 5610b90e6bb21ca31caa635bf0c17c1ee6cf1c08
Patch-mainline: v5.6-rc1
